A spin-off show from the BBC's Antiques Roadshow - Fiona Bruce and experts from Antiques Roadshow turn sleuth as they explore intriguing stories behind family heirlooms. 

S01 - E08 ... Fiona Bruce investigates the story of a Holocaust survivor and visits the Nazi concentration camp, Bergen-Belsen. Seventy years after the liberation of the camp by the British Army, Fiona organises an emotional meeting
